OL,3,CThames Valley Police improves response
OL,4,Cto domestic violence victims
OL,6,FVictims of domestic abuse can now
OL,7,Faccess support more easily and safely
OL,8,Fthanks to a new initiative by Thames
OL,9,FValley Police (TVP).
OL,11,FThrough the new Rapid Video Response
OL,12,F(RVR) service, people wanting to
OL,13,Freport a non-emergency domestic abuse
OL,14,Fincident can speak to an officer via a
OL,15,Fsecure video call from any place they
OL,16,Ffeel safe.
OL,18,FIt means victims can get the help they
OL,19,Fneed quicker and it allows police to
OL,20,Fmake better use of their resources.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
