CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779383153
OL,3,CThames Valley Police improves response
OL,4,Cto domestic violence victims
OL,6,FPolice say RVR is particularly
OL,7,Fbeneficial for victims who may be
OL,8,Funable to attend a police station,
OL,9,Ffear reprisals, or feel anxious about
OL,10,Fofficers turning up at their home
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,FTVP recorded 26,502 domestic abuse
OL,14,Fcrimes between April 2024 and March
OL,15,F2025, and 27,015 between April 2025
OL,16,Fand March 2026 - an increase of 1.9%
OL,17,Fin reported cases.
OL,19,FThe RVR service has been rolled out
OL,20,Fforce-wide, following a successful
OL,21,Fpilot in Oxfordshire last year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
