OL,3,CThames Valley Police improves response
OL,4,Cto domestic violence victims
OL,6,FIt has been used to respond to a wide
OL,7,Frange of incidents, including
OL,8,Fassaults, stalking, coercive or
OL,9,Fcontrolling behaviour, and breaches of
OL,10,Fbail or court orders.
OL,12,FOn average, victims are connected to
OL,13,Fan officer more than nine hours faster
OL,14,Fcompared to traditional deployment
OL,15,Fmethods, according to TVP.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
