OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779383153
OL,3,CThames Valley Police improves response
OL,4,Cto domestic violence victims
OL,6,FTVP's Head of Domestic Abuse and
OL,7,FStalking, Detective Superintendent
OL,8,FHolly Stockwell, said: "Domestic abuse
OL,9,Fcan be incredibly difficult to report,
OL,10,Fand we know that the first interaction
OL,11,Fwith police can shape a victim's
OL,12,Fwillingness to engage with us going
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,15,F"Rapid Video Response allows us to
OL,16,Foffer an immediate, compassionate and
OL,17,Fflexible option, helping us safeguard
OL,18,Fsooner and capture vital evidence at
OL,19,Fthe earliest opportunity.
OL,26,@pD@XOU
