OL,3,CThames Valley Police improves response
OL,4,Cto domestic violence victims
OL,6,FAssessment and Investigation Unit
OL,7,FCrime Manager, Detective
OL,8,FSuperintendent, Michael Bettington
OL,9,Fadded: "By connecting victims with an
OL,10,Fofficer much faster, we are delivering
OL,11,Fa more efficient and effective service.
OL,13,F"It also allows us to make better use
OL,14,Fof our resources, ensuring officers
OL,15,Fare focused where they are most
OL,16,Fneeded, while still providing a high-
OL,17,Fquality response through technology
OL,18,Fand supporting our work to bring
OL,19,Foffenders to justice."
OL,21,FHow to get help...
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@VO]
