OL,3,CThames Valley Police improves response
OL,4,Cto domestic violence victims
OL,6,FThames Valley Police encourages anyone
OL,7,Fwho is a victim of domestic abuse to
OL,8,Freport it.
OL,10,FIf you are in immediate danger and you
OL,11,Fare able to, please call 999.
OL,12,FAlternatively, if you wish to report
OL,13,Fan incident that has happened, then
OL,14,Fplease call 101.
OL,16,FIf you have been affected by issues
OL,17,Fraised in this article, you can
OL,18,Fcontact these organisations for advice
OL,19,Fand support:
OL,21,FNational DA helpline
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
